channel.title: Been trying to register my server for 4 days now
channel.description: This is getting really annoying, I'm doing exactly what everyone is saying for me to do, i port forwarded, my server is running, my friend is even in it right now, and i even tried to register with a proxy, turned off my firewalls, but no matter what i do it always says the server is offline.... can anyone give me help? im using rickscape v5 and i have a linksys router

item.title: Been trying to register my server for 4 days now
item.dc:creator: @Stanyer Stanyer
item.description:
@Stanyer wrote:

Oh right the class isn’t registering with the server properly.

I had this problem too.

Open up “server.java”

Highlight everything, delete it, save, then compile.

Then when you try to add to server status it should work, if it doesn’t, tell me.
